title: Software Engineer Intern
description: At PayPal, I contributed to the development of internal tools designed to test developer APIs and new product releases. My primary project involved creating a mock storefront that simulated a consumer-facing interface, allowing developers to edit and test API endpoints effectively.

title: Software Engineer Intern
description: At Fyve By, an aviation technology startup, I worked on both backend and frontend development for a web application managing hangar scheduling and operations. Additionally, I developed an iOS app integrating Unity for 3D hangar simulations and collision detection to assist ground crews.
